---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Phil Fugate" description="20+ years of engineering, from writing C in college to leading teams at AWS.">
  <article class="about">
    <div class="about-header">
      <img src="/phil.png" alt="Phil Fugate" class="about-photo" width="180" height="180" />
      <h1>About</h1>
    </div>

    <p>
      I'm Phil Fugate — an engineering leader at <strong>AWS</strong> based in Denver, Colorado.
      I've been writing code professionally for over 20 years and managing engineering teams for the
      last several. Currently I'm building and leading a team of software development engineers at AWS.
    </p>

    <p>
      Outside of work, I'm building <a href="/projects">FinEL</a> — a financial analytics platform
      that normalizes SEC filing data to enable cross-company financial comparison. Think Bloomberg
      Terminal, but for the rest of us.
    </p>

    <h2>What I write about</h2>

    <p>
      This site is where I share what I've learned about using AI to dramatically accelerate
      software development. Not theory — I'm writing from the perspective of someone who has shipped
      real infrastructure, real CI/CD pipelines, and real products with AI as a daily collaborator.
    </p>

    <p>
      After 20 years of building software the traditional way, the last couple of years have changed
      everything about how I work. I want to help other experienced engineers make the same leap.
    </p>

    <h2>Background</h2>

    <ul class="timeline">
      <li>
        <span class="year">Now</span>
        <span class="detail">Engineering leader at <strong>AWS</strong>, Denver</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="year">Side</span>
        <span class="detail">Building <strong>FinEL Analytica</strong> — financial data platform</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="year">20+ yrs</span>
        <span class="detail">Full-stack engineering across startups and enterprise</span>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>

    <p>
      I work at AWS. The opinions expressed on this site are entirely my own and do not represent
      Amazon, AWS, or any of its subsidiaries. I'm writing here on my personal time because I
      think these topics matter.
    </p>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>

    <p>
      Find me on <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/philip-fugate" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
      or <a href="https://github.com/pfugate" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .timeline {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .timeline li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .timeline li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .year {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    min-width: 60px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .detail {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
</style>
